OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police are reviewing
OL,7,FCCTV from the day Prime Minister Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer's former chief of staff
OL,9,Fhad his phone stolen, according to
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,FThe loss of ex-top aide Morgan
OL,13,FMcSweeney's phone means that important
OL,14,Fmessages relating to Lord Peter
OL,15,FMandelson's appointment as US
OL,16,Fambassador will not be placed in the
OL,17,Fpublic domain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
