CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774663388
OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FIt comes after MPs moved in February
OL,7,Fto force the publication of tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of documents with the aim of
OL,9,Funcovering how much was known about
OL,10,FLord Mandelson's links to Jeffrey
OL,11,FEpstein before the peer was handed the
OL,12,FWashington job.
OL,14,FConservative Party leader Kemi
OL,15,FBadenoch is among the opposition
OL,16,Fpoliticians who have sought to suggest
OL,17,Fthe phone theft is "fishy".
OL,26,@yD@TOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
