CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774663388
OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FBut Sir Keir said it is "far-fetched"
OL,7,Fto say there was any link between the
OL,8,FMandelson files and the phone theft,
OL,9,Fwhich took place in October, months
OL,10,Fbefore the Commons vote that triggered
OL,11,Fthe collection and release of the
OL,12,Fdocuments.
OL,14,FAccording to The Times, the Met are
OL,15,Fnow reviewing CCTV from Pimlico, the
OL,16,Farea of central London where the theft
OL,17,Fof Mr McSweeney's phone took place, in
OL,18,Forder to establish the facts of the
OL,19,Fcase.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
