OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774663388
OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FMr McSweeney could also be asked for
OL,7,Ffurther clarification as part of the
OL,8,Freview, the newspaper said.
OL,10,FPolice took the unusual step of
OL,11,Freleasing a transcript of Mr
OL,12,FMcSweeney's 999 call reporting the
OL,13,Fphone theft.
OL,15,FThe Met wrongly recorded the theft as
OL,16,Fhaving taken place in east London
OL,17,Frather than Westminster after Mr
OL,18,FMcSweeney wrongly gave his location as
OL,19,FBelgrave Street rather than Belgrave
OL,20,FRoad during the October 20 call.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
