PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774663388
OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FElsewhere, Lord Mandelson will be
OL,7,Fasked to supply messages from his
OL,8,Fpersonal phone as part of the
OL,9,Fdisclosure of files related to his
OL,10,Fappointment as US ambassador.
OL,12,FThe Cabinet Office is working on an
OL,13,Finformation-gathering plan and will
OL,14,Fask the ex-Labour grandee to provide
OL,15,Feverything he holds in scope of the
OL,16,Fhumble address used to compel the
OL,17,Frelease of correspondence, according
OL,18,Fto Government sources.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
