OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774663388
OL,3,CMet Police reviewing CCTV in review of
OL,4,CMorgan McSweeney phone theft
OL,6,FLord Mandelson, a political
OL,7,Fappointment rather than a career
OL,8,Fdiplomat, was sacked from his
OL,9,FWashington role in September last year
OL,10,Fover his links with Epstein, who died
OL,11,Fin 2019.
OL,13,FThe first tranche of documents related
OL,14,Fto the decision was published earlier
OL,15,Fthis month after a demand for
OL,16,Ftransparency by MPs, with more to
OL,17,Ffollow.
OL,19,FMr McSweeney quit Downing Street last
OL,20,Fmonth, with many blaming him for
OL,21,Fpushing Lord Mandelson's appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
